reviewText: I just received and watched this DVD. Although viewable, both the video and audio are not DVD quality; it appears to have been made from a poor quality video cassette recording. The audio is particularly poor, as it is unintelligible in places.Also, there is no scene selection, so if you want to stop in the middle and continue watching later, you have to leave your DVD player on pause.This humorous story deserves a much better DVD.
Title: Book Of Numbers
